{"tid":1150460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：若果中國待他連任後再談判　將面對更苛刻條件","createTime":"2019-05-12T00:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T02:08:21.000Z","uid":5812,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52ff08d5aeee2d11c0c8616fa6e44907c87b10cc","tid":1150460,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:08:32.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在社交網站表示，中國知道他將會在明年的美國總統大選中勝出，當他展開第二個總統任期的時候，中國要與美國達成貿易協議的話，將會面對更加苛刻的條件。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普表示，中國若是聰明的話，現時是時候展坐言起行，不過，他非常喜歡收取大額的關稅。特朗普表示，他覺得中國在近期的貿易談判中節節敗退。<br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普較早前又表示，若果美國公司想避免受關稅問題影響，做法非常簡單，只要在美國本土生產貨品，就能避過關稅。<br />\n<br />\n撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5044db8594a28d1829c126150df4e116db3e2425","tid":1150460,"uid":242917,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:10:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47ee08acee8c714fc5e4e0c059a76df49ee0698a","tid":1150460,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打到你瞓直"},{"pid":"bc0c1dda38a1dcc8439e39a81c1d23897114a45b","tid":1150460,"uid":61688,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"當初全世界以為侵侵得個講字唔敢做"},{"pid":"c213dd899f37290f56fcfe1ba2d5d67ca9156b2d","tid":1150460,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47ee08acee8c714fc5e4e0c059a76df49ee0698a","tid":1150460,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla